---
import { Mail, MessageCircle, Github } from 'lucide-astro';
---
<footer id="contacto" class="bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">¿Listo para modernizar tu negocio?</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">Contáctame para adquirir tu licencia de Zenith POS o solicitar integraciones a medida para tu empresa.</p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-8 mb-12 text-slate-300">
                <a href="mailto:tu-correo@ejemplo.com" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors group">
                    <Mail class="w-6 h-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
                    <span class="font-medium">tu-correo@ejemplo.com</span>
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/1234567890" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors group">
                    <MessageCircle class="w-6 h-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
                    <span class="font-medium">WhatsApp</span>
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/martin-ratti" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-white transition-colors group">
                    <Github class="w-6 h-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
                    <span class="font-medium">GitHub</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">
                    &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Zenith POS Core. Desarrollado por Martin Ratti. Todos los derechos reservados.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>